{{The following documents have been recovered from a datapack captured by the __Project Aidita__[[footnote]] **Translator's Note:** A CN-branch Canon Hub which introduces interaction between multiverses. [[/footnote]] Office. This document seems to describe a color paradigm shift phenomenon on a single individual. Below are these transcribed records.}}

